<section sectnbr = "1D">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "04">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "ASLAP70A1406026" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Demontáž a inštalácia ventila a hlavy valcov
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "ASLAP70A1406025">Komponenty ventilov a hlavy valcov</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "ASLAP70A1406026001">
<title>
Demontáž
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Z vozidla odmontujte zariadenie motora. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406016"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vyberte sacie potrubie. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odmontujte chladiace vodné potrubie. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1606007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odmontujte olejovú vaňu. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odmontujte kryt hlavy valca. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406011"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vyberte kryt rozvodovej reťaze. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406018"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vyberte rozvodovú reťaz. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406023"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vyberte sací a výfukový vačkový hriadeľ. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406013"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 .
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vyberte ložiská vačkového hriadeľa.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uvoľnite skrutky hlavy valcov v takom poradí, ako je uvedené na obrázku, použitím 12-bodového nástrčného kľúča, a potom ich demontujte.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141002.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.080mm" ver = "01" gw = "189" gh = "128"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Skontrolujte okolie hlavy valca kvôli iným častiam potrebným na demontáž alebo odpojenie a demontujte alebo odpojte čokoľvek je potrebné.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vyberte hlavu valca s výfukovým potrubím. V prípade potreby použite zdvíhacie zariadenie.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ak je to potrebné, demontujte z hlavy valca nasledovné komponenty.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Výfukové potrubie: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1B06002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vstrekovací ventil: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1706008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Olejová zátka venturi: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406027"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Zariadenie termostatu: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1606008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "ASLAP70A1406026002">
<title>
Montáž
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "ASLAP70A1406027">Demontáž a opätovná montáž ventilov a hlavy ventilov</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vyčistite styčnú plochu hlavy valca a bloku motora. Odstráňte olej, staré tesnenie a prach zo styčnej plochy.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte zarážacie kolíky (1) do bloku motora.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte nové tesnenie hlavy valcov (2) na blok motora.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141004.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.930mm" ver = "01" gw = "150" gh = "108"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Hlavu valca namontujte na blok motora nasledovne.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Pred vložením hlavy valca, umiestnite kľukový hriadeľ v rozsahu „a“ zobrazenom na obrázku.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Pred dotiahnutím skrutiek hlavy valcov otočte kľukový hriadeľ proti smeru hodinových ručičiek o 30&#176; – 90&#176; tak, ako je to zobrazené na obrázku.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Ak skrutku hlavy valcov používate opätovne, uistite sa, že ste ju skontrolovali, či nie je deformovaná. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406030"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V20A141058.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "37.283mm" ver = "01" gw = "129" gh = "89"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.727in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.727in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.970in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
„a”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
30&#176;
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“b”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
90&#176;
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Pero
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Na nové skrutky hlavy valcov naneste motorový olej.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Pomocou 12-hranného nástrčného kľúča utiahnite skrutky hlavy valcov („1“ – „10“) to 20 N&#183;m (2,0 kgf-m, 15,0 lbf-ft) v číselnom poradí na obrázku.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Tým istým spôsobom ako v kroku b) ich dotiahnite na 40 N&#183;m (4,1 kgf-m, 29,5 lbf-ft).
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Otočte všetky skrutky o 60&#176; v číselnom poradí na obrázku.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Opakujte krok d).
</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T1D018">
<t-part>
Skrutka hlavy valcov*
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-note>
Utiahnite 20 N&#183;m &#8594; 40 N&#183;m &#8594; +60&#176; &#8594; +60&#176; (2,0 kgf-m &#8594; 4,0 kgf-m &#8594; +60&#176; &#8594; +60&#176;, 14,5 lbf-ft &#8594; 29,0 lbf-ft &#8594; +60&#176; &#8594; +60&#176;)
</t-note>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.647mm" ver = "02" gw = "177" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte kľukové hriadele a zdvíhadlo, pričom postupujte podľa krokov 2) a 8) v časti „Inštalácia“ v kapitole 
<intxref refid = "ASLAP70A1406013">Demontáž a montáž vačkového hriadeľa a zdvíhadla ventilu</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nainštalujte rozvodovú reťaz. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406023"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nainštalujte kryt rozvodovej reťaze. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406018"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nainštalujte kryt hlavy valca. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1406011"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nainštalujte olejovú vaňu. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A1506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
